&lt;!-- language: lang-xml --&gt;

     &lt;project&gt;
         ...
         &lt;build&gt;
           ...
           &lt;resources&gt;
             &lt;resource&gt;
               &lt;directory&gt;[your folder containing the class or to be in the classpath here]&lt;/directory&gt;
             &lt;/resource&gt;
           &lt;/resources&gt;
           ...
